sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor AdminUser as Operateur admin
    participant AdminBff as app-admin BFF
    participant ApiTs as app-api-ts
    participant Connectors as app-connectors
    participant Worker as app-api Python worker
    participant Vendor as Vendor API / SFTP
    participant Pg as PostgreSQL
    participant Store as Payload store
    participant Medallion as Bronze/Silver/Gold

    AdminUser->>AdminBff: declencher test/sync integration
    AdminBff->>ApiTs: /api/v1/admin/.../integrations/*
    ApiTs->>Connectors: creation connexion / test / trigger sync
    Connectors->>Pg: persister connection / run / state
    Connectors-->>ApiTs: run queued / status
    ApiTs-->>AdminBff: ack admin

    Worker->>Connectors: POST /v1/runtime/sync-runs/claim
    Connectors-->>Worker: run claimé
    Worker->>Connectors: execution-plan
    alt provider pull
        Worker->>Connectors: access-context
        Connectors-->>Worker: contexte auth + endpoints
        Worker->>Vendor: extraire donnees
        Vendor-->>Worker: payloads source
        Worker->>Connectors: provider-events
    else SFTP pull
        Worker->>Vendor: lire fichiers SFTP
        Vendor-->>Worker: fichiers source
    end
    Connectors->>Store: stocker payloads bruts
    Connectors->>Pg: mettre a jour raw events / sync state
    Worker->>Pg: ingestion / transformations
    Worker->>Medallion: Bronze -> Silver -> Gold
    Medallion->>Pg: ecrire resultats / read-models
    Worker->>Connectors: completed / failed / requeued
